Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.97,VIOLET_1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\yshad6\blur4\frz270\fs90\c&HFAFDF9&\pos(114,649)\4c&HC9A07C&\3c&HCDA687&}朱斯提提亞地區
